graph LR
    DSPO[Data Science Pipelines Operator]

    %% External Dependencies
    DSPO -->|container platform| K8s[Kubernetes/OpenShift 4.11+]
    DSPO -->|workflow engine| Argo[Argo Workflows v3.4+]
    DSPO -->|metadata storage| MariaDB[MariaDB 10.3<br/>Optional]
    DSPO -->|artifact storage| S3[S3-compatible Storage<br/>Required]
    DSPO -->|client SDK| KFP[Kubeflow Pipelines SDK 2.x<br/>Optional]
    DSPO -.->|legacy only| Tekton[OpenShift Pipelines/Tekton 1.8+<br/>DSPv1 only]

    %% External Storage Options
    S3 -.->|production| AWS_S3[AWS S3]
    S3 -.->|production| Ceph[Ceph S3]
    S3 -.->|dev/test only| Minio[Minio<br/>NOT for production]

    %% External Database Options
    MariaDB -.->|production| ExtMySQL[External MySQL/MariaDB]
    MariaDB -.->|production| ExtPostgres[External PostgreSQL]
    MariaDB -.->|dev/test| InternalMariaDB[Internal MariaDB<br/>deployed by operator]

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI Dependencies
    DSPO -->|UI integration| Dashboard[ODH/RHOAI Dashboard]
    DSPO -->|deployment| DSC[ODH Operator /<br/>DataScienceCluster]
    DSPO -->|model serving| KServe[KServe]
    DSPO -->|API access| Workbenches[Workbenches<br/>Notebooks]
    DSPO -.->|optional| ServiceMesh[Service Mesh<br/>Istio]
    DSPO -->|metrics| Monitoring[OpenShift Monitoring]

    %% Integration Points
    Dashboard -->|API calls| DSPO
    Pipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|deploys models| KServe
    Workbenches -->|submits pipelines| DSPO
    DSPO -->|distributed compute| Ray[Ray Clusters<br/>Optional]

    %% Kubernetes Platform Services
    K8s -->|DNS| CoreDNS[CoreDNS]
    K8s -->|storage| CSI[CSI Storage]
    K8s -->|networking| CNI[CNI Plugin]
    K8s -->|auth| RBAC[RBAC]
    K8s -->|TLS| CertManager[OpenShift Service<br/>Serving Certs]

    %% Security & Networking
    DSPO -->|pod-to-pod TLS| CertManager
    DSPO -->|network isolation| NetworkPolicies[Network Policies]
    DSPO -->|external access| Routes[OpenShift Routes]

    %% Build & Deployment
    DSPO -.->|CI/CD| Konflux[Red Hat Konflux]
    DSPO -.->|image registry| Quay[registry.redhat.io]

    %% Styling
    style DSPO fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:4px

    %% External Dependencies
    style K8s fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Argo fill:#999,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style MariaDB fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style S3 fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style KFP fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Tekton fill:#ccc,stroke:#999,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% External Storage/DB Options
    style AWS_S3 fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Ceph fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style Minio fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#999,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style ExtMySQL fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style ExtPostgres fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333
    style InternalMariaDB fill:#e8e8e8,stroke:#999

    %% Internal ODH/RHOAI
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style DSC fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KServe fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style Workbenches fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style ServiceMesh fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5
    style Monitoring fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style Ray fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    %% Kubernetes Services
    style CoreDNS fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333
    style CSI fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333
    style CNI fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333
    style RBAC fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333
    style CertManager fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333
    style NetworkPolicies fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333
    style Routes fill:#e1d5e7,stroke:#333

    %% Build/Deployment
    style Konflux fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#333
    style Quay fill:#d5e8d4,stroke:#333
